{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Implemented (T2 / Phase 1):\n- 3 packaged eval specs added under src/rebar/llm/eval_specs/: completion-verifier (fail/pass; emits_valid_verdict + recall_on_incomplete + no_false_fail_on_complete; judge finding_cites_criterion_and_is_grounded), ticket-quality (finding/pass; emits_valid_review_result + recall_on_seeded_defects + no_fire_on_good_cases; judge finding_is_useful_and_actionable), spec-alignment (finding/pass, BATCH unit spec+epics; recall_on_gaps_and_conflicts + no_fire_on_aligned; judge gap_is_real_and_actionable).\n- Each: generator anthropic:claude-opus-4-8, epochs=3, at_least(2), coverage>=0.8, balanced corpus-tagged datasets (rebar/snap/dso), non-empty gold_set. Repo-state hints live in a 'note' metadata field, NOT in the fed ticket_context/spec (no answer leakage).\n- All 3 pass validate_eval_spec(strict=True); all deterministic scorers are registered (T1); judges are cross-family pinned + gates:false.\n- tests/unit/test_new_eval_specs.py (9 tests): strict-clean, registered scorers, disciplined judges, balanced datasets, non-empty gold. ruff+mypy clean; eval suites green; 'rebar prompt eval completion-verifier' resolves.\nAdvisory triage (plan-review): the E2 'claude-opus-4-8 is a typo' finding is INVALID — Opus 4.8 is a real model id and matches every existing spec's generator convention. Hardcoded thresholds/graceful-degradation/offline-only-proof advisories map to the live-harness task (T4); datasets are seed labels pending human adjudication per the existing eval README convention."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782582443320392001,"uuid":"62851dff-cef7-47ac-a1b6-1dd6fdb72082"}